------------------------------------------------------------
EVENTS IMPLEMENTED
------------------------------------------------------------
  1. Increment/Decrement Counter
     onClick={this.increment} → counter + 1
     onClick={this.decrement} → counter - 1

  2. Multiple Methods on one button (Increase)
     onClick={this.increaseAndSay}
     → calls increment() AND sayHello() together

  3. Event with argument (Say Welcome)
     onClick={() => this.sayWelcome('welcome')}
     → passes 'welcome' string as argument

  4. Synthetic Event (OnPress)
     onClick={this.handleOnPress} → e.type = 'click'
     → displays "Synthetic Event fired! Type: click — I was clicked"

  5. CurrencyConverter (₹ → €)
     onSubmit={this.handleSubmit}
     → 1 INR = 0.011 EUR (e.preventDefault() used)

